== 签署之后 ==
关于这一条约的新闻使得参与[[西姆拉会议|西姆拉会议]]的英国谈判者们担心，俄罗斯可能试图借此机会获得在西藏事务上的影响力<ref name="bell"/>。同时，虽然中国最终没有签署《[[西姆拉条约|西姆拉条约]]》<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.tibetjustice.org/materials/treaties/treaties16.html |title=1914西姆拉会议 |access-date=2008-10-27 |archive-date=2006-04-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060424083824/http://www.tibetjustice.org/materials/treaties/treaties16.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=Goldstein1989-75>The Chinese government initialed but refused to ratify the Agreement. See Goldstein, Melvyn C., ''A History of Modern Tibet'', p75</ref>，蒙古、中华民国政府和俄罗斯还是于1915年5月25日签署了类似的《[[中俄蒙協約|中俄蒙協約]]》。<ref>[http://countrystudies.us/mongolia/26.htm Mongolia - Modern Mongolia, 1911-84] {{Wayback|url=http://countrystudies.us/mongolia/26.htm |date=20101214025324 }}, Country Studies US</ref>这一条约承认了蒙古在国家内政上的完全自治以及俄罗斯在蒙古的特权，同时也正式承认了中国对蒙古的[[宗主权|宗主权]]。<ref>Treaty text quoted from B.L. Putnam Weale, [http://www.fullbooks.com/The-Fight-For-The-Republic-In-China8.html The Fight For The Republic In China] {{Wayback|url=http://www.fullbooks.com/The-Fight-For-The-Republic-In-China8.html |date=20160303165136 }}</ref>

